[src:karmarkar-interior-point/interior-point-method] We can apply path-following methods with the barrier $b(x):=-\sum _{j=1}^{m}\ln(-f_{j}(x)).$ The function b is a self-concordant barrier with parameter *M*=*m*.
[src:karmarkar-interior-point/interior-point-method] The Newton complexity is O(*(m+n)n*2), and the total runtime complexity is O(*m*1/2 (m+n) *n*2).
